工作了十一小時。<br />\n<br />\n支持引入海外醫生番公立醫院齊齊捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果佢地唔去私家嘅話"},{"pid":"880b3abf83df2e302554565b948a595820557eec","tid":1006400,"uid":89861,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e01c166883e78ad92f286992a595e8b133d783a6","tid":1006400,"uid":79930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/542638/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%BF%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F542638%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%2584%259F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25BF%2599&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=5e4a0eb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F542638%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%2584%259F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25BF%2599&h=20f81da1\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/542638/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%BF%99</a><br />\n<br />\n流感高峰期公立醫院病房爆滿，內科是重災區，醫護人員都不滿加床不加人，究竟醫生有多忙？政府再預留五億是否解決到問題？ <br />\n<br />\n這天已經是吳家晴連續第十一日上班，還要工作多三日才放假。家晴畢業後，就是在威爾斯醫院做內科醫生，亦是第四年面對冬季流感高峰期。半小時都沒有，檢查了六名病人。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用了四分鐘，短跑般的速度，終於開始門診。一個上午看了十多名病人，平均一名只有十分鐘。現在約一時四十分，剛剛完成診症。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以吃飯了嗎？還未，因為病人想出院。想不想停下喝水？還未可以，因為很忙。二時十五分，終於拿到飯盒，用了八分鐘就吃完整個飯盒，再走到門診看下午的症。由早上七時半到現在，已經工作了十一小時。<br />\n<br />\n支持引入海外醫生番公立醫院齊齊捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果佢地唔去私家嘅話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"就算走去私家又如何, 多一個人走去私家醫院, 私家醫院就少一個位比依家既公立醫生出去<br />\n又或者多左人出去自己開私家診所, 競爭大, 醫藥費會降低. 唔會迫迺D人係公家 <br />\n而私家醫生收入跌, 公立醫生少左誘因跳出去."},{"pid":"5b206441398472f970129d67074c22c9460ef0e8","tid":1006400,"uid":73200,"like":9,"dislike":13,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4436bc8dd8501fcc7af4b8abcca01011e2ceeac0","tid":1006400,"uid":212796,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e01c166883e78ad92f286992a595e8b133d783a6","tid":1006400,"uid":79930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/542638/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%BF%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F542638%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%2584%259F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25BF%2599&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=5e4a0eb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F542638%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%2584%259F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25BF%2599&h=20f81da1\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/542638/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0%E5%89%8D%E