"},{"pid":"9f10690bb7d64839cf9cacbeb9febaf8966d9a80","tid":1006400,"uid":79930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3a10ef443a3e97247704ed4207986f799cc7eae","tid":1006400,"uid":19725,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e01c166883e78ad92f286992a595e8b133d783a6","tid":1006400,"uid":79930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/542638/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%BF%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F542638%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%2584%259F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25BF%2599&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=5e4a0eb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F542638%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%2584%259F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25BF%2599&h=20f81da1\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/542638/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%BF%99</a><br />\n<br />\n流感高峰期公立醫院病房爆滿，內科是重災區，醫護人員都不滿加床不加人，究竟醫生有多忙？政府再預留五億是否解決到問題？ <br />\n<br />\n這天已經是吳家晴連續第十一日上班，還要工作多三日才放假。家晴畢業後，就是在威爾斯醫院做內科醫生，亦是第四年面對冬季流感高峰期。半小時都沒有，檢查了六名病人。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用了四分鐘，短跑般的速度，終於開始門診。一個上午看了十多名病人，平均一名只有十分鐘。現在約一時四十分，剛剛完成診症。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以吃飯了嗎？還未，因為病人想出院。想不想停下喝水？還未可以，因為很忙。二時十五分，終於拿到飯盒，用了八分鐘就吃完整個飯盒，再走到門診看下午的症。由早上七時半到現在，已經工作了十一小時。<br />\n<br />\n支持引入海外醫生番公立醫院齊齊捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果佢地唔去私家嘅話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:02:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈要求引入中國醫生</span> </span></strong><br />\n五千年黎中國偉大文化 一定要入引中國醫生解決香港班仆街醫生<br />\n好撚唔抵得佢地咁高人工，一定要拉到佢1萬5千蚊一個月 低過洗碗阿姐！！！！！！ 大家一齊跟我大字報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n孕婦剖腹產子被偷腎 中國新華醫院院長供認曾偷九個腎<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20120829/18002608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120829%2F18002608&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=5d51757c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120829%2F18002608&h=24a56f2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20120829/18002608</a><br />\n<br />\n手術後腎消失 農婦尋腎3年無果<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2015/01/29/a1172952.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2015%2F01%2F29%2Fa1172952.html&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=0f78bb0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2015/01/29/a1172952.html</a><br />\n<br />\n包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！ 病人負傷起來繳費<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/882584-中國-包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！+病人負傷起來繳費\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F882584-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%89%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B91%E8%90%AC5%EF%BC%81%2B%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=2791d644\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F882584-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%89%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B91%E8%90%AC5%EF%BC%81%2B%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB&h=c41842b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/882584-中國-包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！+病人負傷起來繳費</a><br />\n<br />\n重慶醫生手術途中突加碼　費用飆升13倍<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20151130/bkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151130%2Fbkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=2efdf98c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20151130/bkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n江蘇男割包皮　醫生手術中加價5倍　院方：沒違規 <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181205/s00004/1543977455217/江蘇男割包皮-醫生手術中加價5倍-院方-沒違規\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181205%2Fs00004%2F1543977455217%2F%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E7%94%B7%E5%89%B2%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B95%E5%80%8D-%E9%99%A2%E6%96%B9-%E6%B2%92%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=b0370d7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181205%2Fs00004%2F1543977455217%2F%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E7%94%B7%E5%89%B2%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B95%E5%80%8D-%E9%99%A2%E6%96%B9-%E6%B2%92%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F&h=3aa50e06\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181205/s00004/1543977455217/江蘇男割包皮-醫生手術中加價5倍-院方-沒違規</a><br />\n<br />\n成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦　警方：嫌犯現已被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/191422/成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦-警方-嫌犯現已被捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F191422%2F%E6%88%90%E9%83%BD%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%89%E5%BE%8C%E7%AB%9F%E8%A2%AB%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E5%AB%8C%E7%8A%AF%E7%8F%BE%E5%B7%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=d895e5da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/191422/成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦-警方-嫌犯現已被捕</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/大國小事/288428/成都無牌醫生將女患者麻醉後強姦-多項罪成獲刑6年4個月\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B%2F288428%2F%E6%88%90%E9%83%BD%E7%84%A1%E7%89%8C%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%87%E5%A5%B3%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%89%E5%BE%8C%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%A4%9A%E9%A0%85%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%916%E5%B9%B44%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7oICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=b6e845f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/大國小事/288428/成都無牌醫生將女患者麻醉後強姦-多項罪成獲刑6年4個月</a><br />\n<br />\n辦案人員經查發現，羅平沒有取得醫師資格證和醫師執業證。他於2017年6月開始在雙流區某街道開設的「1+1服務中心」從事醫療活動，並辦理虛假的醫師資格證、醫師執業證和身份證，向雙流區某醫院提交。他又於2016年至2018年期間，階段性在雙流某醫院坐診。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">強姦、偷腎、加價 、假醫生，少不免 沒事兒</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/re0xvoV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fre0xvoV.gif&h=9fbdef6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強國黨媒展視中國式CPR 救助心臟停頓病人<br />\n－＞未來香港將會獲得優秀中國式醫療！<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUF5Qo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUF5Qo9.jpg&h=7dca3fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建議香港政府先提出引入英國醫生 <br />\n然後再偷偷地引入大陸醫生<br />\n咁樣就可以拉低醫生人工<br />\n我最想見到既事情先會發生！！！<br />\n我要佢地死、低人工過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！</span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n自2012年起，醫管局以有限度註冊聘請了39名海外醫生來港執業，但截至2018年底只有10名仍在公立醫院服務，「事實是醫管局無法挽留本港的畢業醫生，也無法挽留海外畢業的醫生。」<br />\n<br />\n林晢玄早前接受訪問時指，可參考新加坡模式，讓指定院校名單的海外醫生免試到本港公立醫院工作，年期不限。有關建議可謂是「改良版」的有限度註冊制度。<br />\n<br />\n而公共醫療醫生協會今日（30日）再發表聲明，指歡迎任何擁有與本港同等專業資格的海外畢業醫生，遵從現有機制，且透過有限度註冊來港，但需確保海外醫生長期留在公立醫院。<br />\n<br />\n香港公共醫療醫生協會稱，政府在2003年沙士削減2667張病床、推俗稱「肥雞餐」的自願離職計劃、關閉護士學校、削減醫科學額，緊縮醫療開資，而這些措施的惡果終在十多年後出現。協會指香港公營醫療體系早就超出負荷，而醫院的工作環境已達不安全水平，嚴重危害病人安全及影響服務質素，而前線醫護仍一直努力工作，「哀我同業，咫尺但愁雷雨至，向來悲傷何其多？」<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以香港戰地環境引入高質英國醫生！<br />\n可能外國鬼佬鍾意戰地環境同埋語言挑戰</span></strong></span><br />\n大中華呢3個字已經夠吸引佢地<br />\n<br />\n睇下佢地NHS d醫院 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJYOBJo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJYOBJo.jpg&h=b6235a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrxvP3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrxvP3q.jpg&h=62b8bafb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4knr7P6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4knr7P6.jpg&h=d20ccc63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b60UxgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb60UxgO.jpg&h=af70738c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYP95BR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYP95BR.jpg&h=2b03b738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我地香港d醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQWHGas.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQWHGas.jpg&h=eb01e00e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qyJGcg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqyJGcg9.jpg&h=a2c8d832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xsLDXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xsLDXa.jpg&h=ca2fec23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Skczxhm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkczxhm.jpg&h=ed64d856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tjeexhq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeexhq.jpg&h=ac181a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">英聯邦高質醫生一定好鍾意挑戰自己 快d邀請佢地黎香港做野</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"咁你又唔好咁極端<br />\n我支持海外醫生番嚟幫手<br />\n依家問題係公立個環境留唔住佢地<br />\n佢地去私家或自己開診所都好既，起碼公立啲人少啲誘因走<br />\n只不過咁樣嗰effect有啲間接囉，咁樣同原本引入佢地番公立幫手嘅原意有出入，唔efficient"},{"pid":"415bc3720979edd517170f33b13009cd07a15d38","tid":1006400,"uid":22329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b206441398472f970129d67074c22c9460ef0e8","tid":1006400,"uid":73200,"like":9,"dislike":13,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"咁你一定最唔怕辛苦 <br />\n<br />\n快d去做醫生"},{"pid":"8621ccd6ba173218fcd0a73d01d0df569ea532fa","tid":1006400,"uid":79930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48dfc0d2fd6730bd3c662686b6724725ac336802","tid":1006400,"uid":73200,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"ec1c658fb8225594c57c252ee95a9459cdfc8d55","tid":1006400,"uid":19725,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d374a58bcc924ff5455b7f244a31866a75086cce","tid":1006400,"uid":73200,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:09:44.000Z","msg":"喂 師兄 咁荀你都做得架<br />\n考返個dse 幾個5** 讀多6 年醫學院 再做實習醫生你都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隨時歡迎加入！"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T04:17:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T05:15:58.000Z","msg":"巴打......當年呢班高材生準備公開試嗰陣你去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frow